node.text: @eatandtravelwithus yes so flavourful! Pleasures to share too! 😋

Someone can’t wait to eat!😂 Cooked Anchovies Fried Rice for lunch today and sprinkled atop some Chilli Crunch (chilli garlic bits) from Daddy Mikks. It’s so crunchy and addictive!
.

If you like some spice and garlic in your food, then you should give this Chilli Crunch a try! 😋
.

Daddy Mikks is a product of Philippines with no preservatives added. Other condiments available are Garlic Crunch & Chilli Shots, all available at Shopee online and Meat My Grill. . 
Thanks Jen & Jac of Daddy Mikks Singapore for introducing me to these condiments! .
.
.
